title: Google\Cloud\Asset\V1\AnalyzeMoveRequest
name: AnalyzeMoveRequest
description:
The request message for performing resource move analysis.

Generated from protobuf message google.cloud.asset.v1.AnalyzeMoveRequest

Extends Google\Protobuf\Internal\Message

params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.resource
params.description: Required. Name of the resource to perform the analysis against. Only GCP Project are supported as of today. Hence, this can only be Project ID (such as "projects/my-project-id") or a Project Number (such as "projects/12345").

params.name: data.destination_parent
params.description: Required. Name of the GCP Folder or Organization to reparent the target resource. The analysis will be performed against hypothetically moving the resource to this specified desitination parent. This can only be a Folder number (such as "folders/123") or an Organization number (such as "organizations/123").

params.name: data.view
params.description: Analysis view indicating what information should be included in the analysis response. If unspecified, the default view is FULL.
